      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"vibe\" thing is making me nervous lol. You mentioned things getting a \"tangle\" and the \"underbelly\" of the station... it sounds like it could get pretty chaotic. Are you saying there are actual things that cause these random, weird disruptions that aren't just standard delays? Like, is there anything else I should be looking out for besides just signal failures?",
